{"tid":942363,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"好想寫聖誕卡呀 2018","createTime":"2018-12-15T15:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T16:27:08.000Z","uid":38077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7bd490981caea14c2467d8883b1f819163ce94","tid":942363,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"上年同上上年都好多謝各位巴絲賞面俾機會我寫聖誕卡<br />\n<br />\n做咗OT狗成年 照舊希望一切順順利利 屋企同身邊嘅人都可以每日健康同開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩開心唔開心嘅事/想寫嘅嘢 都可以話俾我知<br />\n雖然我可能幫唔到你地啲咩 但起碼可以娛樂你一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到截郵日會一次過寄出<br />\n預早祝大家有個開開心心嘅聖誕同2019<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有上年或者上上年都搵過我寫聖誕卡嘅巴絲 希望你哋填表嗰陣話埋俾我聽 俾我多謝翻你哋呢兩年對我嘅支持同鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13efca5a2ab4d64974e54ba0cc053f092c35b0ca","tid":942363,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18edde406e1e5e91bbc820cd5c54d7afd9ce30a9","tid":942363,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee45371048d768847995dfef5181fd0aeb612b1e","tid":942363,"uid":226244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18edde406e1e5e91bbc820cd5c54d7afd9ce30a9","tid":942363,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"已填form 了，期待👍"},{"pid":"bae3efdc2e99d5d9a8870ecd031692a10b6b9f75","tid":942363,"uid":125073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"